    <!-- imageholder -->
    <div class="text_holder">
     <p class="style2">
      SPANISH WINTER ROCK WEEKEND
     </p>
     <p>
      Join us in the Autumn in Calpe, on the East coast of Spain, for a long weekend of climbing, guiding and tuition.

Learn how to lead climb and improve your climbing technique in the sun, where the weather is almost guaranteed to be amazing everyday!
     </p>
     <p>
      Fly Friday, climb for 5 days and return on the  Wednesday.
     </p>
     <p>
      Cost = £300 per person.
     </p>
     <p>
      Extend your stay and climb for longer. Prices arranged on enquiry. Flights and accommodation are separate.
     </p>
     <p>
      <strong>
       Dates to be confirmed
      </strong>
     </p>
    </div>
    <!-- text_holder -->
